9t all sunshine and rainbows. \n\nBut playdates with friends are, as are library trips, going to museums, camping - we have a circle of close friends and a circle of acquaintances that we very much enjoy hanging out with. \n\nIn fact, my social battery is drained most days now \ud83e\udee3\ud83d\ude06 \n\n#homeschool #homeschoolfun #socialization #homemaking", "hashtags": ["homeschool", "homeschoolfun", "socialization", "homemaking"], "mentions": [], "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DYqTqBNgvjr/", "commentsCount": 2, "dimensionsHeight": 1136, "dimensionsWidth": 640, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-sea5-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/704914325_2173297626841478_5784920413926088426_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-sea5-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=102&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gH_zvc--UJZHyGeJc2vXJeh49SMbQktBdDU4lVDI7qB2OI2jDyM_VeRVMHDTn3IA7A&_nc_ohc=PEds3gKM1MoQ7kNvwFyeycF&_nc_gid=AaM93OAd_Tz6FfVSdYvhEQ&edm=AOQ1c0wBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af_GPstkRVE0pULdRYXoQ4am_6nr3Gux38Al0-O5-cOBVw&oe=6A312EB2&_nc_sid=8b3546", "images": [], "videoUrl": "https://scontent-sea5-1.cdninstagram.com/o1/v/t2/f2/m86/AQPl3l80KDNoP2GYvdiv2UGZyTwl8yG0VqyED_WZ2SqqTqKwoeoY6ok35-KRo1iXTn_2RwcqquqUYb0pqbw5quG87Wv_62Fff5tP8hA.mp4?_nc_cat=109&_nc_sid=5e9851&_nc_ht=scontent-sea5-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_ohc=swP5A1ZowxIQ7kNvwFydrig&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6Inhwdl9wcm9ncmVzc2l2ZS5JTlNUQUdSQU0uQ0xJUFMuQzMuNzIwLmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MSIsInhwdl9hc3NldF9pZCI6MTI3Nzc2OTc4NDU2ODYyMSwiYXNzZXRfYWdlX2RheXMiOjIwLCJ2aV91c2VjYXNlX2lkIjoxMDA5OSwiZHVyYXRpb25fcyI6NTEsInVybGdlbl9zb3VyY2UiOiJ3d3cifQ%3D%3D&ccb=17-1&vs=9ff07f28deb1751&_nc__ofFBBUCKAJDMywXQEmZmZmZmZoYEmRhc2hfYmFzZWxpbmVfMV92MREAdf4HZeadAQA&_nc_gid=AaM93OAd_Tz6FfVSdYvhEQ&_nc_ss=7a3ba&_nc_zt=28&oh=00_Af8kYi8c7IgXgKqs0dBDgz_8hx_8qbpEi3BnLGvVh2kB0g&oe=6A2D4E0A", "alt": null, "likesCount": 117, "videoViewCount": 2790, "timestamp": "2026-05-23T00:32:56.000Z", "childPosts": [], "locationName": "Brighton, Michigan", "locationId": "215895908", "ownerUsername": "slayathomemother", "ownerId": "5511530864", "productType": "clips", "musicInfo": {"artist_name": "The Tams", "song_name": "Be Young, Be Foolish, Be Happy", "uses_original_audio": false, "should_mute_audio": false, "should_mute_audio_reason": "", "audio_id": "617057818659882"}, "isCommentsDisabled": false}, {"id": "3900135356372300108", "type": "Video", "shortCode": "DYgEHFcgzFM", "caption": "TEAMWORK TASKS - as a homeschool mom, we\u2019ve learned a ton about how to manage conflict with each other, with friends, and with new playmates at co-ops or parks. \n\nWhat works at home for us is our new teamwork tasks system \ud83d\ude09. Don\u2019t get me wrong - we still practice working through things, but it\u2019s also important to know how to work together towards a common goal with someone you might not be getting along with perfectly, too.\n\nThis comes up in the future with friends, family, neighbors, spouses, kids, coworkers, etc. \n\nIt isn\u2019t a punishment, either. It\u2019s a redirection. \ud83d\udc4d \n\nIt\u2019s been working really well for us for our 6 year old and 10 year old, as a reference, but I could see it working for kids of almost any age too \ud83d\ude4c\n\nDo you do something similar to this? What\u2019s your go-to system? \ud83d\ude0d\ud83d\udc47\ud83d\udc47\ud83d\udc47\n\n#homeschoolmom #momof3kids #cleaning #cleanhome\ud83c\udfe1 #summertimefun", "hashtags": ["homeschoolmom", "momof3kids", "cleaning", "cleanhome\ud83c\udfe1", "summertimefun"], "mentions": [], "url": "https://www.instagram.com/p/DYgEHFcgzFM/", "commentsCount": 8, "dimensionsHeight": 1136, "dimensionsWidth": 640, "displayUrl": "https://scontent-sea5-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/702191310_1984751202430424_3107556233139711755_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&_nc_ht=scontent-sea5-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=108&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gH_zvc--UJZHyGeJc2vXJeh49SMbQktBdDU4lVDI7qB2OI2jDyM_VeRVMHDTn3IA7A&_nc_ohc=Gtmq34xxXHgQ7kNvwETT6Vr&_nc_gid=AaM93OAd_Tz6FfVSdYvhEQ&edm=AOQ1c0wBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af86yEhw3F0